{"tid":920520,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"1月東京近郊三日兩夜","createTime":"2018-11-29T01:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T13:44:00.000Z","uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1635bcc71d7e1d748da57c94eebee3be32b7c3f4","tid":920520,"uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"小弟打算1月中去東京，去近郊三日兩夜，浸下温泉、睇下風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位ching有咩意見？plan a定plan b好？<br />\n<br />\nPlan A （輕鬆D、時間鬆動，但住箱根好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &yen;24000/人<br />\nDay1 上野&gt;熱海&gt;熱海城&gt;伊豆長岡&gt;伊豆の国パノラマパーク（宿伊豆長岡 &yen;17000/人）<br />\n用埋Jr wide pass 第三日，係東京坐特急落熱海<br />\n<br />\nDay2 伊豆長岡&gt;三島吊橋&gt;箱根神社&gt;元箱根港坐賊船&gt;桃源台港&gt;大涌谷&gt;早雲山 （宿早雲山 &yen;24000/人）<br />\n箱根周遊卷<br />\n<br />\nDay3 早雲山&gt;強羅&gt;彫刻の森美術館&gt;箱根湯本&gt;食完Lunch返新宿shopping （宿上野）<br />\n箱根周遊卷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPlan B （我知好chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\nDay 1 上野&gt;上午去江之島（主要行下大佛+鎌倉）&gt;下午去海熱城（宿伊東 &yen;17000/人）<br />\n用埋Jr wide pass 第三日，係東京坐特急落伊東<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 伊東&gt;城崎海岸&gt;大室山&gt;伊豆シャボテン動物公園&gt;伊東&gt;巴士去伊豆長岡（宿伊豆長岡 &yen;17000/人）<br />\n用cash<br />\n<br />\nDay3 伊豆長岡&gt;箱根神社&gt;元箱根港&gt;坐賊船去桃源台港&gt;大涌谷&gt;早雲山&gt;強羅&gt;箱根湯本&gt;小田原坐JR返上野（宿上野）<br />\n箱根周遊卷"},{"pid":"955f2d8d3c416592ff7610004d7d1ecd0ef9f63f","tid":920520,"uid":10466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:20:41.000Z","msg":"日光個邊幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e509e564863346caad9959a0bbe3b626b523f406","tid":920520,"uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"955f2d8d3c416592ff7610004d7d1ecd0ef9f63f","tid":920520,"uid":10466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:20:41.000Z","msg":"日光個邊幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:25:49.000Z","msg":"日光我都有諗過<img src=\"/ass